The paper proposes a novel approach for disease classification using geometric deep learning and graph signal processing. This work is likely to fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
